<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Help | Kakwara Hospital</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href={~p"/assets/login.css"}>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    .help-card {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
    }
    .help-card h2 {
      color: #005b96;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .faq-list {
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .faq-list li {
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .faq-q {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #005b96;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
      display: block;
    }
    .faq-a {
      color: #333;
      margin-left: 1rem;
    }
    .help-contact {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .help-contact a {
      color: #005b96;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .help-contact a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="login-container">
    <div class="help-card">
      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> Help & FAQ</h2>
      <ul class="faq-list">
        <li>
          <span class="faq-q"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> How do I book an appointment?</span>
          <span class="faq-a">Go to the "Get Started" or "Contact" page and fill out the appointment form, or call our emergency number for urgent care.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="faq-q"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> Can I access my medical records online?</span>
          <span class="faq-a">Yes, registered users can access their records through the Patient Portal after logging in.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="faq-q"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> What should I do in an emergency?</span>
          <span class="faq-a">Call our emergency number immediately: <a href="tel:+254743856988">+254743856988</a>. Our team is available 24/7.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="faq-q"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> How do I reset my password?</span>
          <span class="faq-a">Click "Forgot Password" on the login page and follow the instructions to reset your password.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="faq-q"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> Who can I contact for support?</span>
          <span class="faq-a">You can email us at <a href="mailto:Sehathospital@gmail.com">Sehathospital@gmail.com</a> or use the contact form on the Contact page.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="help-contact">
        <p>Still need help? <a href={~p"/contact"}><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us</a></p>
      </div>
      <a href={~p"/main"} class="home-link" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:1.5rem;padding:0.6rem 1.4rem;background:#005b96;color:#fff;border-radius:6px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,91,150,0.08);transition:background 0.2s;">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-house" style="margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>